data.description: **HUGE PRICE REDUCTION**!!! Beautifully and completely renovated 3-bedroom 2 bathroom home with a huge laundry room that can be used as an additional bedroom making it a 4-bedroom home perfect for a big family. The kitchen offers granite countertops and plenty of cabinetry. The master bedroom features a high ceiling with a skylight allowing the natural light to flow, and French doors leading to the backyard and the cemented patio. This freshly painted home offers many upgrades including, wood laminated floors, renovated bathrooms, decorative brick and wood walls, newer windows, new plumbing, and electrical. The detached 2-car garage can be converted into an ADU. The long cemented driveway can easily fit 4+ cars. Located in one of the nicest neighborhoods in South Gate full of green trees and near the well-known Tweedy Blvd. Close proximity to the 105 and 710 Fwy, transportation, restaurants, stores, and within walking distance to schools.
